spec_data.Name: texlive-countriesofeurope
spec_data.Description:
The bundle provides a font "CountriesOfEurope" (in Adobe Type 1
format) and the necessary metrics, together with LaTeX macros
for its use. The font provides glyphs with a filled outline of
the shape of each country; each glyph is at the same
cartographic scale.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:02:52 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A font with the images of the countries of Europe
